IMMEDIATE — DO THESE NOW
========================================

[ ] DEPLOY: Migrate backend from Render → Fly.io Mumbai
    Follow: docs/BACKEND_DEPLOYMENT_FLYIO.md
    Steps:
      brew install flyctl
      fly auth login
      cd backend && fly launch --no-deploy   # select bom region
      fly secrets set SECRET_KEY="..." DATABASE_URL="..." ALLOWED_HOSTS="gyangrit-backend.fly.dev" ...
      fly secrets set FAST2SMS_API_KEY="your-fast2sms-key"   ← OTP WILL WORK AFTER THIS
      fly secrets set CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS="https://gyan-grit.vercel.app"
      fly deploy

[ ] After Fly.io deploy: update Vercel env var
    VITE_API_URL = https://gyangrit-backend.fly.dev/api/v1

[ ] After Fly.io is confirmed working: delete Render service

[ ] FAST2SMS: Add FAST2SMS_API_KEY to Fly.io secrets (see above)
    OTP SMS will work automatically — services.py is already complete
    No code changes needed — just the env var


